rows.label: tlk70000017_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, hello, you lot! I thank you again for
your invaluable assistance with my
previous inventions.

rows.label: tlk70000017_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You may remember me saying before,
but the parts you can find here differ
greatly than those found in Gula.

rows.label: tlk70000017_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, it's come to my knowledge that
there are some particularly high-quality
parts to be had in Gula.

rows.label: tlk70000017_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I hear you can even get your hands on
gold parts! What I could do with gold...
Just thinking about it makes me drool.
